<h1>API Reference</h1>

<p>Auto-generated reference for every public module exported from the <code>grigson</code> package. Pages are built from TypeDoc output at Eleventy build time.</p>

<ul>
{% for mod in typedocModules %}
<li>
  <a href="{{ ('/dev/api/' + mod.slug + '/') | url }}"><strong>{{ mod.title }}</strong></a>
  — {{ mod.description }}
  {% if mod.functions.length %}
  <br><small>{% for fn in mod.functions %}{% if not loop.first %}, {% endif %}{{ fn.name }}{% endfor %}</small>
  {% endif %}
</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
